{%- comment -%}
  ===========================================================================
  Zooryn — Page "Our Story" (page dédiée, éditable)
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Page complète qui raconte l'histoire de la marque ombrelle Zooryn.
  Bandeau de titre + 4 chapitres (sur-titre / titre / texte) + CTA final.
  Tout est éditable dans Personnaliser. Les chapitres sont des réglages fixes
  (et non des blocks) pour qu'ils s'affichent toujours, même quand la section
  est incluse en statique dans le template page.zooryn-story.liquid.
  Le ticker / header / footer viennent du layout 'sculpted'.
  CSS commun : assets/sculpted.css.

  Pour assigner ce template : Pages > (page Our Story) > Modèle de thème
  → choisis "zooryn-story".
  ===========================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign s = section.settings -%}

<section class="zsp">

  <header class="zsp-head wrap">
    {%- if s.eyebrow != blank -%}
      <p class="eyebrow zsp-eyebrow">{{ s.eyebrow | escape }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if s.title != blank -%}
      <h1 class="display zsp-title">{{ s.title | escape }}</h1>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if s.intro != blank -%}
      <div class="zsp-intro">{{ s.intro }}</div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </header>

  {%- assign hero = s.hero_image -%}
  {%- if hero -%}
    <div class="zsp-hero-wrap wrap">
      <div class="zsp-hero">
        <img src="{{ hero | image_url: width: 1600 }}"
             srcset="{{ hero | image_url: width: 800 }} 800w, {{ hero | image_url: width: 1600 }} 1600w"
             sizes="(max-width:1180px) 100vw, 1180px"
             alt="{{ hero.alt | default: 'Zooryn' | escape }}" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  <div class="zsp-blocks wrap">
    {%- for i in (1..4) -%}
      {%- assign eb  = 'c' | append: i | append: '_eyebrow' -%}
      {%- assign hd  = 'c' | append: i | append: '_heading' -%}
      {%- assign bd  = 'c' | append: i | append: '_body' -%}
      {%- assign c_eyebrow = s[eb] -%}
      {%- assign c_heading = s[hd] -%}
      {%- assign c_body    = s[bd] -%}
      {%- if c_heading != blank or c_body != blank -%}
        <div class="zsp-block">
          {%- if c_eyebrow != blank -%}<p class="eyebrow zsp-b-eyebrow">{{ c_eyebrow | escape }}</p>{%- endif -%}
          {%- if c_heading != blank -%}<h2 class="zsp-b-h">{{ c_heading | escape }}</h2>{%- endif -%}
          {%- if c_body != blank -%}<div class="zsp-b-body">{{ c_body }}</div>{%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>

  {%- if s.cta_heading != blank or s.cta_label != blank -%}
    <div class="zsp-cta-wrap">
      <div class="zsp-cta wrap">
        {%- if s.cta_heading != blank -%}<h2 class="display zsp-cta-h">{{ s.cta_heading | escape }}</h2>{%- endif -%}
        {%- if s.cta_sub != blank -%}<p class="zsp-cta-sub">{{ s.cta_sub | escape }}</p>{%- endif -%}
        {%- if s.cta_label != blank -%}
          <a class="btn btn-accent zsp-cta-btn" href="{{ s.cta_link | default: '/' }}">{{ s.cta_label | escape }}</a>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

</section>

<style>
  .zsp{padding:0 0 8px}
  .zsp-head{max-width:760px;text-align:center;padding-top:72px;padding-bottom:8px}
  .zsp-eyebrow{margin-bottom:16px}
  .zsp-title{font-size:var(--t-hero);margin:0 0 24px}
  .zsp-intro{color:var(--muted);font-size:19px;line-height:1.65}
  .zsp-intro p{margin-bottom:16px}

  .zsp-hero-wrap{padding-top:40px}
  .zsp-hero{position:relative;aspect-ratio:16/9;border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden}
  .zsp-hero img{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}

  .zsp-blocks{max-width:760px;padding-top:48px;padding-bottom:48px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:48px}
  .zsp-block{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:40px}
  .zsp-block:first-child{border-top:0;padding-top:0}
  .zsp-b-eyebrow{margin-bottom:12px;color:var(--accent)}
  .zsp-b-h{font-size:var(--t-h1);line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 18px}
  .zsp-b-body{color:var(--muted);font-size:17px;line-height:1.7}
  .zsp-b-body p{margin-bottom:14px}

  .zsp-cta-wrap{background:#0c0d10;color:#fff;margin-top:24px}
  .zsp-cta{text-align:center;padding-top:72px;padding-bottom:72px;max-width:680px}
  .zsp-cta-h{color:#fff;font-size:var(--t-h1);margin:0 0 14px}
  .zsp-cta-sub{opacity:.85;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 auto 28px;max-width:46ch}
  .zsp-cta-btn{margin:0 auto}

  @media (max-width:749px){
    .zsp-head{padding-top:48px}
    .zsp-intro{font-size:17px}
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Zooryn — Page Our Story",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "text", "id": "eyebrow", "label": "Sur-titre", "default": "Our story" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Titre", "default": "One label. Only what earns its place." },
    { "type": "richtext", "id": "intro", "label": "Intro", "default": "<p>Zooryn started with a simple frustration. Too many brands chase whatever is trending, flood their shelves with products nobody asked for, and hope something sticks. Quality becomes an afterthought, and the customer ends up paying for the guesswork.</p><p>We wanted to do the opposite. Zooryn is a health and sport label built to earn trust one product at a time, where every item has to prove it deserves to carry our name before it ever reaches you.</p>" },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "hero_image", "label": "Image (16:9, ex. 1600 × 900)", "info": "S'affiche en grand bandeau sous l'intro." },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Chapitre 1" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c1_eyebrow", "label": "Sur-titre", "default": "The idea" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c1_heading", "label": "Titre", "default": "Built around how you actually move" },
    { "type": "richtext", "id": "c1_body", "label": "Texte", "default": "<p>Zooryn is built on one belief: your gear should make you feel stronger in your own body. On the pitch, at the gym, or simply walking out the door, what you wear should work with you, never against you.</p><p>We design for real life and real bodies, not for a glossy catalogue. Every piece has to do a job, look the part, and feel right the moment you put it on. If it does not change how you move or how you feel, it has no reason to exist.</p>" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Chapitre 2" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c2_eyebrow", "label": "Sur-titre", "default": "How we work" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c2_heading", "label": "Titre", "default": "One product at a time" },
    { "type": "richtext", "id": "c2_body", "label": "Texte", "default": "<p>We do not drop a hundred products and hope. We test one at a time, in the real world, and keep only the ones that genuinely perform. If a product does not earn its place, it never makes it to you.</p><p>It is a slower way to build a brand, and that is the point. Every item under Zooryn goes through the same test: would we wear it ourselves, every single day? Only the ones that pass make it to the shelf, which means a smaller range, but a range you can actually trust.</p>" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Chapitre 3" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c3_eyebrow", "label": "Sur-titre", "default": "What we stand for" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c3_heading", "label": "Titre", "default": "Health, sport and everyday confidence" },
    { "type": "richtext", "id": "c3_body", "label": "Texte", "default": "<p>From compression wear that helps you feel comfortable in your own skin to match-day protection that lets you play without holding back, Zooryn lives at the meeting point of health, sport and confidence.</p><p>We are not here to sell you a lifestyle or a fantasy. We are here to make a few things genuinely well, so that the moment you put them on, you stand a little taller and move a little freer. Confidence is not loud. It is just knowing your gear has your back.</p>" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Chapitre 4" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c4_eyebrow", "label": "Sur-titre", "default": "Where we're going" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "c4_heading", "label": "Titre", "default": "Earning our place, every day" },
    { "type": "richtext", "id": "c4_body", "label": "Texte", "default": "<p>Zooryn is young, and we like it that way. It means every decision still matters, every product still has to fight for its spot, and every customer still gets our full attention.</p><p>As we grow, the rule will not change. We will keep testing in the real world, keep cutting what does not work, and keep raising the bar with every product that carries our name. The goal was never to be the biggest. It is to be the one you reach for first.</p>" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Appel à l'action (bas de page)" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_heading", "label": "Titre CTA", "default": "Gear that earns its place" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_sub", "label": "Sous-titre CTA", "default": "Discover the products we put our name on." },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_label", "label": "Bouton CTA — texte", "default": "Shop Zooryn" },
    { "type": "url", "id": "cta_link", "label": "Bouton CTA — lien" }
  ],
  "presets": [ { "name": "Zooryn — Page Our Story" } ]
}
{% endschema %}
